
mod_subreqonly - Apache 2 module to hide resources from normal requests
                 allowing access only to sub-requests

Homepage: 
   http://www.mad-hacking.net/

Building:
   Run:
      $ ./configure --with-apxs=/usr/sbin/apxs
      $ make
      $ make install

Configuration:
   Edit httpd.conf and add:
      LoadModule subreqonly_module modules/mod_transform.so

   Simple usage:
      AddOutputFilter SubReqOnly xslt
      SubReqOnlyOptions AllowApacheFS

   Would hide all xslt files from all but ApacheFS sub-requests.
